body.p:
To affect the highlighted text from the content, use the
        oxy-comment-hl element (or oxy-delete-hl,
        oxy-insert-hl,
      respectively):oxy-comment-hl {
  color:magenta;
}

body.codeblock:
oxy-range-start:before {
  display:inline;
  content:'[' attr(hr_id) ']';
  color:red;
}
oxy-range-end:before {
  display:inline;
  content:'[/' attr(hr_id) ']';
  color:red;
}
